Package: MS2extract
Type: Package
Title: Targeted MS2 Spectra Extraction for In-house Compound Library Creation
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2023-06-08
Authors@R: c(
    person("Cristian", "Quiroz-Moreno",
           email = "cristianquirozd1997@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9069-9147") ),
    person("Jessica", "Cooperstone",
           email = "cooperstone.1@osu.edu",
           role = c("aut"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7920-0088") )
           )
Maintainer: Cristian Quiroz-Moreno <cristianquirozd1997@gmail.com>
Description: A mass spectrometry toolbox with the objective of importing mass spectrometry
   data, and extracts the desired MS2 spectra.
   Subsequently, users can export the spectra in a .msp file format, as a resulting
   compound database for further use in compound identification tasks.
